Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.32,0:00:06.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间  空间和物质\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}giving birth to an endless
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.63,0:00:09.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始不断膨胀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}expanding existence of time, space and matter.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:13.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每天  我们都在解密这神秘莫测\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Every day, new discoveries are unlocking the mysterious,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.16,0:00:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人疯狂的极端之地\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the mind-blowing, the deadly secrets of a place
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.06,0:00:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宇宙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}we call the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:23.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日全食\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A total eclipse.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.92,0:00:26.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一瞬间  光辉万丈的太阳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The brilliant sun suddenly obliterated
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.02,0:00:28.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,消失在月亮的暗面中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}by the black disk of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.64,0:00:33.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像一颗眼珠正俯视着你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}You can see this eyeball looking down at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.04,0:00:36.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日食既令人叹为观止  又让人惊心动魄\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Both breathtaking and frightening,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.54,0:00:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它预示着2012年的太阳大风暴\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}eclipses warn us of powerful solar storms
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.68,0:00:44.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可能使地球大混乱的古老预言成为现实\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that may fulfill an ancient prophecy of chaos on Earth in 2012.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.58,0:00:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类会陷入极度恐慌\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}People would freak out.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:49.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无法制冷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We wouldn't have refrigeration.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.20,0:00:50.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不再有照明\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}We wouldn't have lights.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.53,0:00:55.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遥远恒星的日食现象揭示了新行星的存在\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Eclipses of distant stars are now revealing new planets,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.61,0:00:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中甚至有类地行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}even other Earths.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.88,0:00:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些行星出其不意地出现在我们视野中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some of them just popped right out at us.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.97,0:01:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,探寻的范围包括整个宇宙空间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The search covers the entire universe,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.94,0:01:04.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,却发端于地球表面\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}but it begins here on Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.09,0:01:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,此时太阳正隐没在日全食中\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as the Sun hides its face in total eclipse.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.41,0:01:32.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个天空中的奇观\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's a spectacle in the sky
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:38.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数千年来  人类为之着迷\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that has enthralled human beings for thousands of years.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.22,0:01:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了  开始了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here it comes. Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.59,0:01:41.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here it comes.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:45.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,开始了  看那黑影\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Here it comes. The shadow.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.13,0:01:47.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日全食\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A total eclipse of the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.20,0:01:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有幸看见的人将对此永生难忘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Few people who see one will ever forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.75,0:02:07.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亲眼目睹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Personally witnessing
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.75,0:02:11.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日全食的亲身体验\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a total solar eclipse in the flesh
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.25,0:02:13.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(43,205)}{\an4}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\b0}{\fsp0}{\c&HFFFFFF&&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&&}艾力克斯·菲利潘科\N加州大学伯克利分校
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.45,0:02:13.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一次神奇而令人敬畏的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}is an amazing, awe-inspiring,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.96,0:02:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又极为感动的经历\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}tremendously moving experience.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.13,0:02:19.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从没有其他经历给我这样的感受\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}I've never experienced anything quite like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.63,0:02:25.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有些人  如天文学家格伦·施奈德\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Some, Like astronomer Glenn Schneider,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.83,0:02:27.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是一小群不分时间地点在全球奔波\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}are part of a sub-culture of globe-hopping
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.00,0:02:34.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,追逐日食现象的人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}eclipse chasers who will go anywhere, anytime to see an eclipse.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.11,0:02:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日食很吸引人  因为当天色变暗时\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It grips you, because the sky has gone dark,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.12,0:02:44.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并不像午夜那么黑  而像是浓重的日暮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}not as dark as midnight, but like a very deep twilight.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.49,0:02:50.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就像一颗眼珠正俯视着你\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you can see this eyeball looking down at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.99,0:02:51.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(43,205)}{\an4}{\fn微软雅黑}{\fs14}{\b0}{\fsp0}{\c&HFFFFFF&&}{\3c&HFFFFFF&&}格伦·施奈德\N亚利桑那大学
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.76,0:02:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太阳表面的黑影正是月球的轮廓\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The black disk where the Sun was is the silhouette of the Moon.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:00.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,令人难以置信的是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It's an experience that you can't believe
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.67,0:03:03.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,整个过程仅持续一两分钟\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}it was only a minute or two minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.84,0:03:08.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,恍如漫长一生  实则短短一瞬\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It seems to have lasted a lifetime and also just an instant.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.38,0:03:20.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个令人振奋的现象是太空探索的起点\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}This compelling event is a launching pad for cosmic exploration,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.66,0:03:28.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藉此将解开一系列长久困惑着人类的奥秘\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}solving a string of mysteries that have puzzled mankind for ages.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.20,0:03:32.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是什么让太阳在毫无征兆的情况下消失呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}What makes the Sun disappear without warning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.00,0:03:34.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种现象何时发生\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}When does it happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.57,0:03:36.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们如何预测它\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}How can we predict it?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.20,0:03:39.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人类能否自己制造日食\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Can we make it happen ourselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.37,0:03:42.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这些问题一旦得到解答  我们会发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Once understood, we find that each eclipse
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.08,0:03:45.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次日食都提供了关于宇宙的全新信息\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}reveals something new about the universe.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.21,0:03:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今我们在寻找远恒星的最新日食现象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Even now, we're finding our newest eclipses around distant stars,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.75,0:03:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,并发现太阳系外行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}revealing extra-solar planets,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.49,0:03:55.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其中可能有类地行星\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some, perhaps twins to the Earth,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.72,0:03:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拥有孕育生命的可能\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}with the potential for life.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.37,0:04:07.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,故事记载始于地球上的日食之谜\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The story begins with the mystery of our own eclipses,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.74,0:04:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,即光天化日之下  太阳突然间消失\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a sun suddenly vanishing in broad daylight.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.91,0:04:16.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早在有历史记载之前\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Visible since before recorded history,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.11,0:04:20.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的祖先对日食充满了好奇与恐惧\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}the ancients regarded eclipses with wonder and fear.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.82,0:04:25.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古人没有客观地意识到\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The ancient people didn't understand physically
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.15,0:04:28.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,日食是怎样一种现象\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}what was going on during a solar eclipse.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.56,0:04:33.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们看见的是太阳上逐渐变大的缺口\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}They would see a progressively bigger bite being taken out of the Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,似乎天神或毒龙吞咬着太阳\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as though some gods or dragons were eating the Sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.10,0:04:39.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向人类表达他们的愤怒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}mad at those people.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.57,0:04:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此人们击打锅碗瓢盆\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}So the people would beat pots and pans
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.17,0:04:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大声喊叫甚至以处女祭祀\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and yell and scream and sacrifice virgins
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.01,0:04:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以诸如此类的行为来平息神怒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and all sorts of things to appease the gods
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.18,0:04:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或吓跑毒龙\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and scare the dragons away.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.65,0:04:51.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,结果呢\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And you know what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:53.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每次都奏效了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It worked every time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.72,0:05:00.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,数千年来\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Through thousands of years,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.19,0:05:04.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过对天空中日月轨迹的耐心观测\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}patiently watching the movements of the Sun and the Moon in the sky,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.79,0:05:07.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古代的天文学家们终于明白\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}ancient astronomers realized eclipses happen
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.63,0:05:10.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当月球运转到太阳正前方时日食便发生了\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}when the Moon passed directly in front of the Sun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.00,0:05:19.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最后学者们通过对日食规律的长期研究\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In time, scholars studied the patterns of eclipses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.58,0:05:21.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已能预测其发生的时间\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}long enough to predict them.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.15,0:05:32.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早在22个世纪前 古巴比伦人\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Babylonians discovered what's called the Saros cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.95,0:05:35.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就发现了沙罗周期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}more than 22 centuries ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沙罗周期就是日食周期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Saros cycle is a cycle of eclipses
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个周期每223个月循环一次\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that repeat every 223 months,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.60,0:05:44.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也就是18年一轮\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}roughly every 18 years,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.60,0:05:47.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,每个周期之间都非常相似\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}and they're very similar to one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.47,0:05:51.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古希腊人了解到了古巴比伦人的这一发现\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The Greeks were aware of the Babylonian discovery,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.51,0:05:57.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这一点从安提凯希拉装置上就能看出\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}as we've learned from the remarkable antikythera mechanism,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.95,0:06:04.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,它出自1901年地中海海底的沉船\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}an ancient device found on a shipwreck under the Mediterranean sea in 1901.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:09.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安提凯希拉装置一开始被认为是\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The antikythera mechanism was first thought to be
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.32,0:06:12.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某种时间计或天体计时器\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}some sort of a clock and then some sort of celestial timer.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.50,0:06:16.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个极为复杂的装置\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}It was a very complex mechanism
