Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:38.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,用于测算行星的运动轨迹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}for calculating movements of the planets,
