Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.09,0:06:45.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但最近的发现令他们瞠目结舌\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But the latest discovery astounded them.
