Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.42,0:06:55.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发现这个装置里\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}they found that the Babylonian Saros cycle
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.11,0:06:58.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,包含了古巴比伦的沙罗周期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}was built into the device.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.07,0:07:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,该装置的两块底板上刻有\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}In two of the back plates of the mechanism was inscribed
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.61,0:07:11.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一个有着分区的螺旋形标志\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}a spiral-like figure that had divisions,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.09,0:07:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把它们放在一起\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}that when you added them up,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.59,0:07:16.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对应的就是沙罗周期的月份\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}corresponded to the months in a Saros cycle.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:21.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把沙罗周期包含到该装置里的唯一原因\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The only reason to have the Saros built into the mechanism
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.70,0:07:24.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是该装置也应用于预测日食\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}was if it was an eclipse predictor as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.67,0:07:32.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,平均每16个月就可以在地球上\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}A total eclipse of the Sun can be seen somewhere on Earth
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.22,0:07:35.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个位置看到一次全日食\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}an average of once every 16 months.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.08,0:07:42.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如今  预测日食已是精确的科学\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}Today, predicting them is a very exact science.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:47.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,美国本土下一次可见的日全食\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}The next total solar eclipse to be visible
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.16,0:07:52.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将发生在2017年8月21日\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}from the United States will be on August 21, 2017.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.43,0:07:56.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如今的天文学家能够提供的\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}But modern astronomers can do much better
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:07:58.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已不仅仅是日食的日期\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}than supplying the date for an eclipse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.07,0:08:02.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一张日食地图显示出了人们在2017年\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}An eclipse map shows the exact path
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.44,0:08:06.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够看到的日全食的精确轨迹\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}along which people can see the 2017 total eclipse.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.34,0:08:11.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,时间精确到秒\N{\fnCronos Pro Subhead\fs14\1c&H3CF1F3&}And the timing is down to the second.
